name: LONELY HEARTS Vol. 4 ''Void''
description: Void is an ancestral Lonely Heart, he has been part of the brigade almost since its foundation. Due to his magical qualities, he has defeated mortality and systematically helped to improve the existence of interplanetary beings thanks to his vast and ancient occult knowledge. He is currently on the planet PV-3000, known for the high magical energy emanated by the crystals of his lands. His search for truth and progress has led him to develop a new way of understanding power and energy. But he is cunning and cautious, knowing that there are many minds in the galaxy, and beyond, who could use this new science for evil.
